text: Latkowski or Łatkowski (feminine: Łatkowska, plural: Łatkowsky) is a Polish- language surname. Notable people with the name include: *Daniel Latkowski (born 1991), a German footballer *Klaudiusz Łatkowski (born 1985), a Polish professional football player *Mariusz Latkowski (born 1982), a Polish bobsledder Category:Polish-language surnames
